  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Pathological comparisons of surgical open lung biopsies and cryobiopsies in non-IPF ILD.
      Patients with non-IPF ILD eligible for an open lung biopsy will undergo cryobiopsy in the
      same time. Between observers agreement will be assessed for each pairs of samples.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
