  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>The percentage of concordant diagnoses between cryobiopsy and surgical lung biopsy.</measure>
    <time_frame>for statistical analysis, 12 months after the first inclusion</time_frame>
    <description>The gold standard is the consensual diagnosis between the two readers established from surgical biopsy</description>
  </primary_outcome>
