  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Non IPF ILD eligible for surgical lung biopsy reviewed during multidisciplinary
             approach

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Ineligible for lung biopsy: pulmonary hypertension, coagulation deficiency, FEV&lt;11,
             giant emphysematous bullae, hemodynamic instability severe hypoxia, general anesthetic
             ineligibility
      </textblock>
